headline: Baron Real Estate Fund Decreased its Holdings in D.R. Horton (DHI) on Share Price Appreciation
summary: Baron Funds, an investment management company, released its “Baron Real Estate Fund” fourth quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund increased 12.46% (Institutional Shares) in the full year compared to a 7.49% return for the MSCI US REIT Index (the REIT Index) and a 12.70% return for […]
